OL,3,CBiker's plea: Please look out for us
OL,5,FA biker from Wallasey, left in
OL,6,Fpermanent pain after a crash, has
OL,7,Freleased photographs of her injuries
OL,8,Fin the hope it encourages car and van
OL,9,Fdrivers to be mindful of more
OL,10,Fvulnerable road users.
OL,12,FElaine Velho was a passenger on a
OL,13,Fmotorbike riding past the Royal Oak on
OL,14,FHigh Street, Bromborough, in Summer
OL,15,F2022, when she was hit by a car coming
OL,16,Fout of a side road.
OL,18,FShe was flung onto the road along with
OL,19,Fthe rider, leaving them both battered,
OL,20,Fbruised and in need of hospital
OL,21,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
