OL,3,CBiker's plea: Please look out for us
OL,5,F"I was incredibly lucky that I got
OL,6,Faway without any broken bones, because
OL,7,FI was completely armoured up in full
OL,8,Fleathers. I had a concussion, and
OL,9,Ffacial bruising even with a helmet on.
OL,10,FI still have pain in my left shoulder,
OL,11,Fright hip, a contusion in my left
OL,12,Fcalf, and my ribs were so badly
OL,13,Fbruised I couldn't move."
OL,15,FElaine, 58, and the rider of the bike
OL,16,F- who suffered a broken arm - were
OL,17,Ftaken to Arrowe Park hospital for
OL,18,Ftreatment. The driver of the car was
OL,19,Funharmed, Elaine said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
