OL,3,CBiker's plea: Please look out for us
OL,5,FThe mum-of-two, who is a member of
OL,6,FMotorcycle Action Group (MAG) which
OL,7,Fcampaigns on behalf of bikers across
OL,8,Fthe UK, said the incident left her
OL,9,Fnervous of large vehicles coming out
OL,10,Fof side roads. She was forced to take
OL,11,Fa break from the roads, and traded in
OL,12,Fher high-powered motorbike for a
OL,13,Fsmaller, less powerful version.
OL,15,FTwo years on, Elaine says a new
OL,16,Fnational campaign to encourage drivers
OL,17,Fto remain aware of motorcyclists on
OL,18,Fthe roads is long overdue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
