OL,3,CBiker's plea: Please look out for us
OL,5,FShe said: "Bikers do the same driving
OL,6,Ftest as car drivers, but then you have
OL,7,Fto take two tough modules about
OL,8,Fsafety, blind spot checks, because we
OL,9,Fknow we're vulnerable road users. We
OL,10,Fknow we take the risks, but
OL,11,Fincreasingly we're seeing drivers on
OL,12,Fmobile phones. A lot of drivers and
OL,13,Fother road users don't look for
OL,14,Fmotorbikes - they're looking for a
OL,15,Fmuch bigger vehicle.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
