OL,3,CBiker's plea: Please look out for us
OL,5,F"There used to be campaigns on TV
OL,6,Fabout looking out for bikes, but now
OL,7,Fwe don't see anything. Because
OL,8,Fmotorcyclists are one of the most
OL,9,Fvulnerable users on the roads, a
OL,10,Fcampaign to increase awareness and
OL,11,Fencourage drivers to make sure people
OL,12,Fare looking out for motorbikes is
OL,13,Fneeded.
OL,15,F"The average age of bikers I know is
OL,16,F65 to 70. We're not joy riders or
OL,17,FHell's Angels. We're just a bunch of
OL,18,Fbikers who meet in New Brighton on a
OL,19,FSaturday and go for rides when we can
OL,20,Fin Wales or Lancashire."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
