OL,3,CBiker's plea: Please look out for us
OL,5,FShe added: "I still have pain in my
OL,6,Fleft knee, right hip, left shoulder,
OL,7,Fand I've still got a bit of a scar on
OL,8,Fmy head. But the psychological impact
OL,9,Fis far more damaging. I've been
OL,10,Fdriving 37 years and even now I have
OL,11,Fissues with people coming out from the
OL,12,Fleft. I have never been a nervous
OL,13,Fdriver, but things like that have an
OL,14,Fimpact."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
